Well, I haven't exhausted you, I have.

52:07.880 --> 52:09.643
Really, I'm delighted we were able to do this.

52:09.984 --> 52:15.814
It's wonderful insights.

52:17.937 --> 52:19.879
because there's a lot of material.

52:19.919 --> 52:23.463
Yeah, and it'll be a nice companion to my earlier work.

52:23.723 --> 52:42.223
Yes, but I think if you do get in touch with these emigre libraries that still exist, I mean, there's a Ukrainian one in New York, and the Lithuanian one, and the Lithuanian one, those are the

